data.description: One owner home located on a one acre lot just west of Highway 15 and County Road 47.  Home has a three-car attached garage plus detached 24x24 garage.  Perfect for all the toys.  4 Bedrooms/2 Baths with open floor plan.  Generous sized Master Bedroom.  Vaulted ceiling.  Hardwood and ceramic tile flooring.  Granite countertops in Kitchen and Bath.  Two level deck for entertaining.  14'x14' hot tub room off the back of the garage with patio and fire pit.  Rocori and Kimball school district is an option as well as St. Cloud.
